Animations for different stances (walk, run, stand, greet)

Object spawn avoid collision

Settlements improvements:
- Streets
- NPCs living there
- Procedural houses

Improved Settlement connections:
- Connect new settlements only to closest ones around.
- All settlements should have at least one road to each other settlement.
- Use heuristic to determine if new road should be made.
- Roads follow terrain. Closest path to destination uses objects crossed as weight for heuristic function. Making straight path not always the best.

